<div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/59b79e43c808695a2c55911edd3331bb2.png"></span><span>Hallowed Auspex III</span></dt><dd><div>Grants the user an Auspex gauge. The Auspex<br>gauge fills when the user's first or second skills<br>are used. When the gauge is completely filled,<br>it grants the user the "Twilight Moon" effect.<br>When this effect is active, it grants the user<br>a unique force strike with five increasingly<br>powerful charge levels. This effect cannot stack,<br>and will be consumed on use.<br><br>Also, using Glorious Sanctuary will grant the user<br>a defense amp with a maximum team amp level<br>of three. After this amp is granted, this ability will<br>not grant it again for 30 seconds.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/89cfb88183671a67f82c3ae2993958d42.png"></span><span>Sacred Shield III</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to poison and curses<br>by 100%. When the user is hit by an attack<br>that would have poisoned or cursed them,<br>their strength is increased by 15% for 10 seconds.<br>This increase will not stack, and, after activating,<br>this buff cannot be activated again by the same<br>affliction for 15 seconds.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/5664a5d55b1fc3ad7b0ef31de2647f502.png"></span><span>Auspex's Prayer III</span></dt><dd><div>When an ability increases the user's HP,<br>their strength will increase based on the<br>amount of HP gained. This bonus strength<br>will be reduced if the user is below max HP,<br>relative to the amount of HP lost, and will<br>return if they are healed. This strength buff<br>is not triggered by HP increases from<br>co-abilities and chain co-abilities.<br><br>Also, when the user has a defense amp,<br>increases the potency of recovery skills by 10%.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. The stats shown here represent the adventurer at level 100 with 70 mana nodes unbound.</div><div>2. The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities.</div><div>3. The stats for the adventurer included in this notification shown in any prior notifications or preview videos were the stats at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unbound.</div><div>4. When an adventurer&#39;s skill level increases, the skill gauge will fill more slowly when set as a shared skill.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1644300000,update_time1644206600